  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Provide Clean Water to Rural Communities in Kumbo</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The local communities and SELF RELIANCE PROMOTERS (SeReP) have identified a serious need following the collapse of the lone water scheme, Kumbo Water Authority, due to crisis. This project serves entire villages, supports health centers, primary schools, and secondary schools to fight against water-related diseases which come as a result of the absence of treated water. It will reduce the distance of fetching clean water, improve health and living standards for 6000+ inhabitants around Kumbo.</narrative>
  </description>
